data.description: Welcome home to 546 W Peachtree Street!!! Sitting on a generous lot size, at almost half an acre, this completely renovated 2 bedroom 2 full bath bungalow, minutes to downtown Woodruff will be sure to WOW you! The 10ft+ ceilings, along with the open floor plan give this home a much larger and spacious feeling. The all new windows provide a substantial amount of daylight which further adds to the beauty. In the kitchen, you will find all new shaker cabinets along with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and an island providing additional cabinet storage. All new laminate floors can be found throughout the home along with ceramic tile found in the completely renovated bathrooms. The master bedroom boasts a large WALK-IN closet. The decorative fireplaces add to the charm of this fantastic bungalow. HVAC and roof is completely new providing you an additional peace of mind. Schedule your showing today! This one wont last!!
